berg.com/news/articles/2023-06-08/ google-contract-staff-that-helped-train-ai-seek-to-unionize?sref=ExbtjcSG&quot;>;根据&lt;em>;彭博&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;的报告。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id =&quot;JYxwON&quot;>;当其中一名承包商提交...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23950392/google-contractors-accenture- obscene-bard-prompts-unionizing&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23950392/google-contractors-accenture-obscene-bard-prompts-unionizing" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23950392/google-contractors-accenture-obscene-bard-prompts-unionizing</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry></feed>